{"tid":2354370,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"黎緊新KPOP女團又有台灣妹。。。","createTime":"2021-01-05T12:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T10:08:16.000Z","uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"51d6bd5e8c73c7500a89f4ff55b0d95a1897cf29","tid":2354370,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T12:11:03.000Z","msg":"知名製作人新沙洞老虎與環球音樂共同推出的7人新女團<br />\n預定將於2月正式出道<br />\n團名:TRI.BE<br />\n(完美的象徵'Triangle'的'TRI'加上有'存在'意思的'Be'，擁有'完美的存在'的意味)<br />\n<br />\n查了一下原來去年就已經公開了練習生<br />\n之前的代稱叫Lion Girls<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKim SongSun (金頌善)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/3K0Qjus.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F3K0Qjus.jpg&h=b1076f61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1997.03.22 A型<br />\n<br />\nKelly (林韋希) 台灣人(高雄)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/iQhz5qk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FiQhz5qk.jpg&h=ef043cad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2002.01.16 A型<br />\nVLOG <a href=\"https://youtu.be/TdMWlFY5B1g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTdMWlFY5B1g&d=QL2FFPepynYtbGyOTzoAG4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=2547f4ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TdMWlFY5B1g</a><br />\n(參加過中國選秀&quot;青春有你2&quot;)<br />\n<br />\nKim JinHa (金今夏)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/XdzMpjY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FXdzMpjY.jpg&h=b317aee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2003.11.21 O型<br />\n<br />\nBang SoEun (方素恩)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/9RvWrMC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2F9RvWrMC.jpg&h=43143130&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2005.12.10 AB型<br />\n<br />\nJIA (郭嘉佳)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/XkxrZbH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FXkxrZbH.jpg&h=90785a23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2005.07.30 A型<br />\n<br />\nKim HyunBin (金賢彬)<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/8cLc